{"word":"G1921 - ἐπιγινώσκω - epiginṓskō - ep-ig-in-oce'-ko - Acknowledge","slug":"G1921","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιγινώσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epiginṓskō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-ig-in-oce'-ko"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Acknowledge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x03B3;&#x03B9;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03C9; - epigino&#x0304;sko&#x0304;</b> - <i>ep-ig-in-oce'-ko</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G1097\">G1097</a>; to <i>know upon</i> some mark, that is, <i>recognise</i>; by implication to <i>become fully acquainted with</i>, to <i>acknowledge:</i> - (ac-, have, take) know (-ledge, well), perceive."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1097\">G1097</a>, <a href=\"#/G1106\">G1106</a>, <a href=\"#/G1107\">G1107</a>, <a href=\"#/G1108\">G1108</a>, <a href=\"#/G1110\">G1110</a>, <a href=\"#/G176\">G176</a>, <a href=\"#/G1922\">G1922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2607\">G2607</a>, <a href=\"#/G4267\">G4267</a>, <a href=\"#/G4268\">G4268</a>, <a href=\"#/G4774\">G4774</a>"}]}